It's slow 1 hander so it suffers from a very small min damage bonus, it's also extremely heavy at 15 wgt. <br>
Go with a centi longsword. It's a much better weapon and they are very common and cheap. <br>
On veeshan you can pick one up for 1k or less now.<br>
Another good weapon is the jagged blade of mourning.<br>
13/25 I think +stats. They sell for 2-3k on veeshan.<br>
<br>
Of course, I would really suggest you not spend any cash on a 1 hander and go the 2 hander route since you are losing huge amounts of damage output for small ac gains. They may seem big, but trust me it's small compared to your loss in damage output.<br>
